file.name: keyValue.v1.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: keyValue
  version: '1.0'
  contact:
    name: urykhy
    email: urykhy@gmail.com
servers:
  - url: 'http://localhost:3000/api/v1'
paths:
  '/kv/{key}':
    get:
      summary: Get value
      tags:
        - KeyValue
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            application/octet-stream:
              schema:
                type: string
                format: binary
          headers:
            etag:
              schema:
                type: integer
        '404':
          description: Not Found
      operationId: get-kv-key
      parameters: []
    parameters:
      - schema:
          type: string
        name: key
        in: path
        required: true
    put:
      summary: Put value
      operationId: put-kv-key
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
        '201':
          description: Created
        '412':
          description: Precondition Failed
      parameters:
        - schema:
            type: integer
          in: header
          name: If-Match
        - schema:
            type: string
          in: header
          name: If-None-Match
      tags:
        - KeyValue
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/octet-stream:
            schema:
              type: string
              format: binary
    delete:
      summary: Delete value
      operationId: delete-kv-key
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
        '404':
          description: Not Found
        '412':
          description: Precondition Failed
      tags:
        - KeyValue
      parameters:
        - schema:
            type: integer
          in: header
          name: If-Match
    head:
      summary: Check if value exists
      operationId: head-kv-key
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          headers:
            etag:
              schema:
                type: integer
        '404':
          description: Not Found
      tags:
        - KeyValue
  /kx/multi:
    get:
      summary: Multi Get
      operationId: get-kx-multi
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  type: object
                  properties:
                    key:
                      type: string
                    value:
                      type: string
                    timestamp:
                      type: integer
      tags:
        - KeyValue
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: array
              items:
                type: string
    put:
      summary: ''
      operationId: put-kx-multi
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: array
              items:
                type: object
                properties:
                  key:
                    type: string
                  value:
                    type: string
                  timestamp:
                    type: integer
      tags:
        - KeyValue
    delete:
      summary: ''
      operationId: delete-kx-multi
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: array
              items:
                type: string
      tags:
        - KeyValue
components:
  securitySchemes:
    BearerAuth:
      type: http
      scheme: bearer
tags:
  - name: KeyValue
security:
  - BearerAuth: []
